Package Model

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
Model.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
This is a class for holding information about an appointment.

    This method is a constructor for an appointment.
    Appointment(String appType, int appMonth, int appCount)
    This method is an alternative, overloaded constructor for an appointment object, specifically this appointment is the count of appointments, grouped by type and month, used in Report 1.

      public Appointment(int appID, String appTitle, String appDesc, String appLocation, String appType, String appStartDateTime, String appEndDateTime, int appCustomerID, int appUserID, String appContact)
      This method is a constructor for an appointment.
      Parameters:
      appID - - the appointment ID
      appTitle - - the appointment title
      appDesc - - the appointment description
      appLocation - - the appointment location
      appType - - the appointment type
      appStartDateTime - - the appointment start date and time in String format
      appEndDateTime - - the appointment end date and time in String format
      appCustomerID - - the Customer ID of the Customer associated with this appointment instance
      appUserID - - the User ID of the User associated with this appointment instance
      appContact - - the Contact associated with this appointment instance

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(String appType, int appMonth, int appCount)
      This method is an alternative, overloaded constructor for an appointment object, specifically this appointment is the count of appointments, grouped by type and month, used in Report 1.
      Parameters:
      appType - - the type of appointments
      appMonth - - The month of the appointments
      appCount - - the count of the appointments
